Ling Chen is waiting for you up ahead.

135
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:04,230
Copy that.

136
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,720
I'll leave then.

137
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:15,830
♪I look out the window♪

138
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,480
