197
00:09:08,670 --> 00:09:09,470
Idiot.

198
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:10,470
Come down.

199
00:09:12,150 --> 00:09:12,710
What happened?

200
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:14,710
